# console/assets/ — minified/bundled JS/CSS build artifacts produced by Vite.
# These files contain third-party library strings (e.g., lucide-react, Radix UI
# docstrings) that may embed marketing prose from upstream authors. The SPA source
# is scanned in web/src/**; scanning compiled bundles is redundant and produces
# false positives from upstream vendor code.
